column1: Categorical division of reversal errors ( Ferry et al., 2000) - digging in the dish that did not contain the food pellet ( S -) ( error of commission; Fig. 5A) versus failing to respond within 3 - min of presentation ( error of omission; Fig. 5B) revealed that both genotypes chiefly committed errors of commission versus errors of omission ( D2R - / - mice, U = 0. 00; p < 0. 01; D2R + / + mice U = 9. 00, p < 0. 05), D2R - / - mice committed more commission errors than D2R + / + mice ( U = 5. 00, p < 0. 05), and there were no differences between D2R - / - and D2R + / + mice in omission errors ( U = 27. 5, p = 0. 65).
